            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="21314512">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">本章英文原名：Tiananmen。
第三段英文原文是“There is no dispute about the denouement, however. After hesitating for seven weeks and exhibiting serious divisions within its ranks over the use of
force, the Chinese leadership cracked down decisively on June 4. The General Secretary of the Communist Party, Zhao Ziyang, was dismissed. After weeks of internal debates, Deng and a majority of the Polit...</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21314512/">(<span class="">14回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-09-24 16:58</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">21人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                本章英文原名：Tiananmen。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>第三段英文原文是“There is no dispute about the denouement, however. After hesitating for seven weeks and exhibiting serious divisions within its ranks over the use of<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>force, the Chinese leadership cracked down decisively on June 4. The General Secretary of the Communist Party, Zhao Ziyang, was dismissed. After weeks of internal debates, Deng and a majority of the Politburo ordered the PLA to clear Tiananmen Square.”被中文版压缩为一句话“最终，经过几周的内部争论后，政治局平息了抗议活动。”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







