            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="21661052">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">倒数第三段最后一句“同时，布什恳求中国这位最高领导人理解美国公众的愤怒情绪，这是美国理想主义的自然流露”。恳求？原文“urged”有规劝、敦促的意思，绝非什么“恳求”。另外，这句之后，引用了布什致邓小平私信的一段：
“I ask you as well to remember the principles on which my young country was founded. Those principles are democracy and freedom—freedom of speech, freedom of assemblage, freedom from arbi...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-10-11 16:30</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                倒数第三段最后一句“同时，布什恳求中国这位最高领导人理解美国公众的愤怒情绪，这是美国理想主义的自然流露”。恳求？原文“urged”有规劝、敦促的意思，绝非什么“恳求”。另外，这句之后，引用了布什致邓小平私信的一段：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>“I ask you as well to remember the principles on which my young country was founded. Those principles are democracy and freedom—freedom of speech, freedom of assemblage, freedom from arbitrary authority. It is reverence for those principles which inevitably affects the way Americans view and react to events in other countries. It is not a reaction of arrogance or of a desire to force others to our beliefs but of simple faith in the enduring value of those principles and their universal applicability.”<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>这一段被中文版完全删除。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







